title: Watch Japanese Alt-Rock Trio TsuShiMaMiRe Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents TsuShiMaMiRe performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded September 26, 2024.

Songs:
SHOW YOU MY SOY SAUCE 00:32
24030番地に回覧板を回せ 05:17
Sex On The Beach 07:49
迷曲 -MEIKYOKU- 10:59
Double Punch Kick 15:02

Mari Kono - Lead Vocals, Guitar
Yayoi Tsushima - Vocals, Bass
Maiko Takagi - Vocals, Drums

Host: Diana Ratsamee
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs 
Guest Audio Engineer & Mixer: Christian Mock
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Leah Franks & Scott Holpainen 
Editor: Luke Knecht
